race.comment: DEWANA STAR (2) is yet to be beaten here, scoring three wins from as many starts. Comes off a (24.90) win last time, scoring by 4 lengths in a Special conditions H over 450m at this track. Appeals as a leading chance in this. ANALYZATION (1) goes very well this trip starting 11 times for seven wins and three minors. Recorded a 3.5 lengths win (25.03) in a Special conditions H last time at this track. Can hit the frame with the right run. CRACKERJACK KEV (7) was in the minor money with a solid 25.36, finishing third in a Special conditions H at this track last start. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. ELITE ONE (4) comes into calculations after placing at this track and distance most recently.
